#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.trapz:32
msgid ""
"Definite integral of `y` = n-dimensional array as approximated along a "
"single axis by the trapezoidal rule. If `y` is a 1-dimensional array, then "
"the result is a float. If `n` is greater than 1, then the result is an `n`-1 "
"dimensional array."
msgstr ""

